@startuml

title Codegen entity meta-model — SQL (structural)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Entity <<metaclass>> {
  +sql : SQL
}

class SQL <<segment>> {
  +tablename : string
  +parentIdColumn : string [0..1]
  +hierarchyNameField : string [0..1]
  +extraDrops : SqlPasteBlock
}

note right of SQL
  parentIdColumn and hierarchyNameField
  are present only when the non-structural
  HasParentId feature is selected -- see
  this page's UVL feature diagram, which
  carries the matching cross-reference.
end note

class SqlPasteBlock <<PasteBlock>> {
  ID
}

Entity --> SQL
SQL --> SqlPasteBlock

@enduml
